e much more usefui, and we could then ignore our already wasted short term snare/dm which none of us have the gem slot to load.<br><br>Still, no reason this cannot go for more hits, more time.&nbsp;&nbsp; As an added note, even though I think we&nbsp; badly need some highly desired group utility spell like panther, I do not wish to be casting a&nbsp; short term group buff every 5 minutes if I can get away with itl.&nbsp; As it is 15 minutes base can tend to be annoying at times and make it seem like we are constantly changing out spell slots.<br><br><br><br><br><br><br></blockquote>
				
